{
  "stem": "24885.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The inner city was.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, it wasn't because my uncles and my cousins didn't live near us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They lived more-- when we went to visit them, it was just like here.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If it was 10% or 20%, I don't recall.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was spread out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the farmers and everything else was in Polish hands, landowners.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Jewish people from way back were in business mostly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "When you went down on [NON-ENGLISH] Street, the store were strictly Jewish stores.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But very-- even in my time, very seldom did you see Jewish people or more-- less Jewish people with beards and the Jewish caps and so on, than from what I read now and what I understand happened many years before this.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were more modern, even my own cousins.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father's-- one of the oldest brother who had nine kids, and there were four sons.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Only one son was with a beard, the yeshiva.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The rest of them were modern like today, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The story I can remember, one Sunday, my mother's brother came to visit us from Warsaw on the train.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my uncle, who had a small little beard-- which I showed you in the picture-- and my uncle criticized him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they laughed and joked with him because Europeans were very courteous people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When you came on a bus or train, if a family saw an older person come in-- doesn't have to be old, older than 30 or 40-- and they share the-- kids sit and she made them stand up and give the seat.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Well my uncle got a seat right away, my mother's brother.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But my other uncle didn't because he was a little beard.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know there was a difference.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Jewish people were treated differently.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "No two ways about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
